              .gpb-07 style="width: #{get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_miscellaneous"], @candidate["out_total"])}"
                span = get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_miscellaneous"], @candidate["out_total"])
          .gp-bar
            p
              | 返還捐贈：
              span 
                = to_ten_thousands(@candidate["out"]["out_return"])
            .graphic-body
              .gpb-08 style="width: #{get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_return"], @candidate["out_total"])}"
                span = get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_return"], @candidate["out_total"])
          .gp-bar
            p
              | 繳庫：
              span 
                = to_ten_thousands(@candidate["out"]["out_exchequer"])
            .graphic-body
              .gpb-09 style="width: #{get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_exchequer"], @candidate["out_total"])}"
                span = get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_exchequer"], @candidate["out_total"])
          .gp-bar
            p
              | 公共關係費用：
              span 
                = to_ten_thousands(@candidate["out"]["out_public_relation"])
            .graphic-body
              .gpb-10 style="width: #{get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_public_relation"], @candidate["out_total"])}"
                span = get_percentage(@candidate["out"]["out_public_relation"], @candidate["out_total"])
      - else
        .api-dead-block
          | 唉呀！目前從立委投票指南抓取資料失敗，如果想要瀏覽相關資料請直接至立委投票指南查看。
          br
          = link_to "馬上來去看看", "http://vote.ly.g0v.tw/legislator/pc/#{@legislator.id}/#{@ad.id}/", target: "_blank"

  .reply-message
    #disqus_thread
